lead_paragraph: Sevilla edged closer to a berth in the Champions League knockout stages after a solid performance gave the Spanish side a 4-0 home win over 10-man Croatian title holders Dinamo Zagreb in Group H on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Sevilla Thump Dinamo 4-0 to Close In on Last-16 Berth
